text: :For Fats Waller composition, see Handful of Keys Handful of Keys is a song written and performed by Swedish pianist and composer Robert Wells. It was released in Sweden and entered the Swedish Singles Chart straight in at #1 on 17 July 2009, where it stayed for 1 week. ==Charts== ===Weekly charts=== {|class="wikitable" !Chart (2009) !Peak position |- |} ===Year-end charts=== {| class="wikitable" !Chart (2009) !Position |- |Sweden (Sverigetopplistan) |align="center"|74 |} ==References== Category:2009 singles Category:Number-one singles in Sweden Category:2009 songs
